1983;;Careful, He Might Hear You;;Australian;;Carl Schultz;;Wendy Hughes, Robyn Nevin;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Careful,_He_Might_Hear_You;;The film stars Wendy Hughes and Robyn Nevin as two sisters who are locked in a custody battle over their young nephew, PS, played by Nicholas Gledhill. PS has been raised by his aunt Lila (Nevin) and her husband George since his mother died soon after his birth. When Lila's richer sister Vanessa (Hughes) returns from overseas, she seeks custody of PS, citing the opportunities she can give him.